{"tid":2379853,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"康山花園兩房730萬沽 14年賺價2.5倍","createTime":"2021-01-25T13:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T12:52:35.000Z","uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a7cb293e067b796fcf40291836e34a8d956a44c5","tid":2379853,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:05:52.000Z","msg":"康山花園兩房730萬沽 14年賺價2.5倍<br />\n20:15 2021/01/25<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......鰂魚涌康山花園6座低E室，實用面積約431平方呎，屬兩房間隔，望內園景。單位近日以730萬元成功沽出，折合實用面積呎價約16,937元。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，原業主於2007年3月，以約210萬元(已補地價)購入上述單位，持貨多年，現轉手帳面獲利約520萬元，物業升值約2.5倍......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2861592/%E5%BA%B7%E5%B1%B1%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E5%85%A9%E6%88%BF730%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%2014%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%BA%E5%83%B92.5%E5%80%8D?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2861592%2F%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2588%25BF730%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B2%25BD%252014%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E5%2583%25B92.5%25E5%2580%258D%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=46830e9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2861592/%E5%BA%B7%E5%B1%B1%E8%8A%B1%E5%9C%92%E5%85%A9%E6%88%BF730%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%2014%E5%B9%B4%E8%B3%BA%E5%83%B92.5%E5%80%8D?mtc=60037</a>"},{"pid":"56b60b0586f20f1bc72c541c319e575363ec535b","tid":2379853,"uid":4826,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:08:52.000Z","msg":"反手聖光劍 向上劈呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784f44bceec93e9b33f8a2ef1833877d1723c09c","tid":2379853,"uid":37874,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:11:48.000Z","msg":"即係月供一萬 樓價就平均升兩萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets